commit_message:
move GET /v3/catalog to GET /v3/auth/catalog

Moves this call as described by Jamie Lennox's proposal (this follows patchset 1):
  https://review.openstack.org/#/c/107325/

Example request & response:

$ http get http://localhost:35357/v3/auth/catalog \
  --x-auth-token="PKIZ_eJxVV***AaDko="
{
    "catalog": [
        {
            "endpoints": [
                {
                    "id": "52112dccf98049509c2babc885863557",
                    "interface": "public",
                    "region": "regionOne",
                    "url": "http://localhost:5000/v2.0/"
                },
                {
                    "id": "d6e649a6638a4cf195776730ff8fa687",
                    "interface": "admin",
                    "region": "regionOne",
                    "url": "http://localhost:35357/v2.0/"
                }
            ],
            "id": "e33f10957f08415cbbb9bdf828a4de41",
            "name": "Keystone",
            "type": "identity"
        }
    ],
    "links": {
        "self": "http://localhost:35357/v3/auth/catalog"
    }
}

Blueprint: get-catalog
Change-Id: Ia4afdc19190cdbbab2bdeb47990a136a59f053a2

